Github:https://github.com/3289david/ismyblog&lt;p&gt;Your blog. Nothing else.&lt;p&gt;A minimal, self-hosted blogging platform. One blog per account, no post or visitor limits on the free plan. Pro is a single $25/year plan — AI writing tools, premium themes, custom CSS, advanced analytics, newsletter, redirects, webhooks, and API access.&lt;p&gt;Stack
Next.js 16 (App Router, Turbopack), React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4
SQLite via Prisma 7 (driver adapter: @prisma/adapter-better-sqlite3)
Resend for transactional email (verification, password reset, newsletter)
Cloudflare API for automatic .ismy.blog DNS provisioning
Tor ControlPort for automatic per-blog .onion addresses
OpenRouter for AI writing tools (cheap models, e.g. Qwen — configurable)
Polar.sh for billing (Pro is a single $25/year subscription product)
Email + password auth with mandatory email verification (no third-party auth provider)
AI features(AI auto posts a post every day and also get help from AI when writing)
and much more!!!&lt;/p&gt;
